column10:
After a few years of avoiding this game due to the initial bugs and not having enough spare time to sit down and enjoy this game.  I finally came back due to owning a VR headset (Meta Quest 2) and I can honestly say;

It is epic flying through the valleys on the top gun content, and carrying out some bush flying even without the VR.  Once you nail all the controls and menu navigation its fast and easy to get going.

If you have any other flight simulator, you need to get this one.  I assure you, its better (Short of having a 6axis sim)
